<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"GCPEDIA_Privacy\">GCPEDIA Privacy</span></h2>
<p>The Government of Canada is committed to protecting your privacy online. The privacy notice summarizes how we treat your personal information, allowing you to make informed choices about the personal information that you provide to us. For more information read the <a href=\"/gcwiki120-Mo/index.php/GCPEDIA:Privacy_policy\" title=\"GCPEDIA:Privacy policy\" class=\"mw-redirect\">GCPEDIA Privacy Notice</a>.
